20:34.806 --> 20:36.526
medival wet t-shirt contest.

20:38.371 --> 20:41.294
Good news. We took a vote.
And made you, the new King.

20:41.419 --> 20:43.865
And we took an other vote
and you're died.

20:43.990 --> 20:45.535
Gloriously in battle.

20:46.022 --> 20:48.453
Listen fellas, I own you a apollogy

20:48.578 --> 20:51.666
I've been working out on personal stuff.
And I acted like a jerk.

20:53.544 --> 20:55.003
I hope I can make up to you.

20:58.197 --> 20:59.757
Rest in peace, King Ted.

21:01.302 --> 21:04.262
He means, you're dead
so don't come back.

21:04.930 --> 21:08.431
- I got it.
- ***

